title: THSE Szabadkikötő
text:
Tintahalak Sportegyesület Szabadkikötő is a professional <a href="association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Sashalom">Sashalom</a>, <a href="Budapest">Budapest</a>, Hungary, that competes in the <a href="Nemzeti%20Bajnoks%C3%A1g%20III">Nemzeti Bajnokság III</a>, the third tier of <a href="Hungarian%20football%20league%20system">Hungarian football</a>.
History.
THSE Sashalom is going to compete in the <a href="2017%E2%80%9318%20Nemzeti%20Bajnoks%C3%A1g%20III">2017–18 Nemzeti Bajnokság III</a>.
On 12 August 2017, Sashalom beat <a href="Csepel%20FC">Csepel FC</a> 2–1 at the <a href="B%C3%A9ke%20t%C3%A9ri%20Stadion">Béke téri Stadion</a>, <a href="Csepel">Csepel</a>, <a href="Budapest">Budapest</a> on the first matchday of the <a href="2017-18%20Nemzeti%20Bajnoks%C3%A1g%20III">2017-18 Nemzeti Bajnokság III</a> season.
